How much are the delivery charges?
Nlytn provides free delivery on all items if your total order amount is Rs. 3000/- or more. Otherwise Rs. 99-100/- is charged as delivery charges depend on product.
What is the estimated delivery time?
The estimated time of delivery is mentioned on every page. It may differ from one item to another. Please read below for an explanation of delivery estimates:
			Mentioned as 5-7 days delivery time: These items will also be mentioned as "In Stock". For all areas serviced by reputed couriers the delivery time will be 5-7 business days. For other areas, orders will be sent by Registered Post through the Indian Postal Service which may take 1-2 weeks depending on the location. Business days exclude public holidays and sundays.
Mentioned as more than 5-7 days delivery time: We procure and ship the items within the time specified on the item details page.
How will the delivery be done?
We process all deliveries through reputed couriers.
If there is no courier service available in your area, we will ship via Speed post.
Does Nlytn ship internationally ?
For international orders please send email to
contact@nlytn.in
What about warranty and hidden costs (sales tax, octroi etc.)?
There are no extra taxes, hidden costs or additional shipping charges. The price mentioned on the website is the final price. What you see is what you pay. Our prices are all inclusive. All taxes are included with the list prices.
