Can I modify my order after placing it?
Order can be modified of single or multiple items within 24 hrs from the time of the order placed. Please get in touch with customer care at contact@nlytn.in immediately.
When will I receive my refund for a cancelled order?
We shall process your refund immediately once your order has been cancelled. Any coupons applied on the order will be reinstated to your wallet account; any cash back used with this order will be refunded. Your refund shall be in the form of credits to wallet account.
However if you wish to have the amount refunded to your bank account please get in touch with our customer care executive. Only customers who have paid via debit can avail this option.
Why was my order canceled? Why didn't you send me any intimation?
This could be because either the product is out of stock or it has been rejected for quality reasons. An email is always sent when an order is cancelled, but it is possible that it might have gone into your spam folder.
